---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Homepage"
  description="Portfolio of Sara Ringkow Petersen"
  ogtitle="SRP portfolio - homepage"
  ogdescription="Portfolio-site for Sara Ringkow Petersen"
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <div id="cursor"></div>
  <section id="hero" class="relative container md:max-w-3xl max-w-md mx-auto md:text-left text-center py-20">
    <!-- Content of Hero Section (kept on top with z-index) -->
    <div class="relative z-10">
      <h1 id="hero-title" class="font-bold text-gray-300 tracking-wider md:pt-52 pt-32">Hey there!</h1>
      <h2 id="hero-subtitle" class="font-medium text-gray-300 mt-4 mb-12 tracking-widest">Welcome to my portfolio</h2>
      <p id="hero-text" class="text-gray-300 mt-6 leading-7 mx-auto">
        Hi! <br class="md:hidden block" /> I'm Sara Ringkow Petersen, an aspiring multimedia-designer with a strong passion for creating engaging and accessible
        digital experiences. Further down the page, you can read a bit about who I am, look through some of my projects&mdash; highlighted or not &mdash;or
        simply reach out if you have any questions or just want to say hi. <br /><br />Use the navigation menu to navigate around to the different
        sections or subpages, or click the button down below to go directly to my projects.
      </p>
      <div id="hero-button" class="button-container">
        <a
          href="#projects"
          class="relative z-10 text-gray-300 bg-site-red font-bold rounded-lg text-sm px-6 py-3 inline-flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden group mt-8 transition duration-300 uppercase"
        >
          <span class="button-text text-sm relative z-10 w-full text-center uppercase">View projects</span>
          <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-600 transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0"></span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- About Section -->
  <section id="about" class="container mx-auto md:pt-32 pt-10 px-4">
    <div class="bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-80 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center">
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:pr-8">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-300 md:text-left text-center">About me</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-7 md:text-left text-center">
          As a multimedia-designer, I <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">specialise</span> in UX and web design, with a strong
          focus on <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">accessibility</span> and inclusive design. I have a deep understanding
          of the meaning of design, its impact on usability, and the overall importance of creating visually engaging and user-friendly interfaces. As
          someone who's <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">late-diagnosed</span>
          with autism, I know what it's like to be a person who's not fully capable of certain things and have limited understanding of the world around
          them. This has led me to my <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">main goal</span>&mdash; to create digital
          experiences that are accessible and inclusive for all users, regardless of their disabilities.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-7 md:text-left text-center">
          <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">Creativity</span> is at the heart of everything I do, driving me to explore the
          world of design with enthusiasm and curiosity. Each project
          <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">presents a chance</span> to transform ideas into meaningful experiences. I thrive
          on the excitement of
          <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">experimenting with new techniques</span> and discovering innovative ways to bring
          concepts to life. As I journey through this ever-evolving field, I look forward to <span
            class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">embracing new challenges</span
          > and forging connections that <span class="highlight-text text-site-red font-bold text-lg">inspire</span> growth and creativity. The future
          holds endless possibilities, and I'm eager to see where this path will lead me.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex justify-center lg:w-1/2 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
        <img src="images/pfp.webp" alt="About Me Image" class="w-48 h-48 md:w-[350px] md:h-[350px] rounded-full shadow-md object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Values Section -->
  <div id="values" class="pt-10 md:pt-32">
    <section class="container mx-auto py-6 px-4">
      <div class="bg-gray-700 bg-opacity-80 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-300 text-center md:text-left">Values & mission</h3>
        <p class="values-text mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-7 text-center md:text-left">
          My journey in design is guided by principles of accessibility, creativity, and inclusivity, ensuring every user has an exceptional
          experience.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-8">
          <!-- Value Item 1 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mt-1">
              <p class="hidden md:block">1</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-10">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Accessibility first</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">
                I believe in designing for everyone, creating <br class="md:hidden block" /> experiences that are accessible to all users, <br
                  class="md:hidden block"
                /> regardless of ability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Value Item 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mt-1">
              <p class="hidden md:block">2</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-10">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">User-centered design</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">
                My goal is to create intuitive, user-friendly <br class="md:hidden block" /> interfaces that resonate with users and serve their needs.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Value Item 3 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold mt-1">
              <p class="hidden md:block">3</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-10">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Continuous growth</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">
                I am committed to learning and evolving with new <br class="md:hidden block" /> design trends and technologies to push <br
                  class="md:hidden block"
                /> boundaries in digital experiences.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <!-- Skills Section -->
  <div id="skills" class="md:pt-32 pt-10">
    <section id="skills" class="container mx-auto py-6 px-4">
      <div class="bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-80 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-300 text-center md:text-left">Skills & tools</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-7 text-center md:text-left">
          Hereâ€™s a quick overview of my skills, tools, and technologies that I use to bring digital experiences to life.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-8">
          <!-- Skill Item -->
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">H</p>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-4 text-gray-300">HTML & CSS</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Skill Item -->
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">JS</p>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-4 text-gray-300">JavaScript & frameworks</p>
          </div>
          <!-- Skill Item -->
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">UX</p>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-4 text-gray-300">UX & UI Design</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Skill Item(s) -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-8">
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">F</p>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-4 text-gray-300">Figma & Canva</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">P</p>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-4 text-gray-300">Photoshop & Illustrator</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">Git</p>
            </div>
            <p class="ml-4 text-gray-300">Git & GitHub</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <!-- Workflow Section -->
  <div id="workflow" class="">
    <section id="workflow" class="container mx-auto py-6 px-4">
      <div class="bg-gray-700 bg-opacity-80 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-300 text-center md:text-left">Process & workflow</h3>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-7 text-center md:text-left">
          I follow a structured process to ensure every project meets its full potential, from concept to final design.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-8">
          <!-- Workflow Step 1 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">1</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Planning & strategy</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">
                Creating a to-do list to get an overview of the project <br class="md:hidden block" /> and what needs to be done.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Workflow Step 2 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">2</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Research & discovery</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">Understanding the project-goals, audience, and challenges.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Workflow Step 3 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">3</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Design & development</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">Creating wireframes, prototypes, and final design-elements.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Workflow Step 4 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">4</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Coding & testing</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">Building the project from the ground up.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Workflow Step 5 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">5</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Final testing & feedback</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">
                Gathering feedback and refining to <br class="md:hidden block" /> achieve the best user-experience.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Workflow Step 6 -->
          <div class="flex items-start">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-site-red rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold">
              <p class="hidden md:block">6</p>
            </div>
            <div class="ml-4">
              <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-300">Deployment</h4>
              <p class="text-gray-300 md:text-lg text-sm">Deploying the project to production.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
  <!-- Projects Section -->
  <div id="projects" class="md:pt-32 pt-10">
    <section id="project-section" class="container mx-auto px-4 bg-gray-800 bg-opacity-70 rounded-lg shadow-lg mt-8">
      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold max-w-4xl mx-auto text-gray-300 md:text-left text-center pt-12 pb-4">Highlighted projects</h3>
      <p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 leading-7 max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-[2rem] md:text-left text-center">
        I have worked on a lot of different projects in the past, each different in its own way. However, some of them are not as important as others.
        When taking this sort of course, you're bound to have both favorite and least favorite projects. Because you can't always decide what kind of
        project you have to do. I've decided to highlight some of the projects that I'm most proud of.
      </p>

      <div id="projects-grid" class="flex flex-col items-start max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-4 mb-8">
        <div class="w-full md:text-left text-center">
          <em class="text-gray-400 text-lg">Click on the boxes corresponding to each project to see more.</em>
        </div>

        <!-- Button Container -->
        <div class="flex md:justify-start justify-center w-full">
          <a
            href="/other"
            class="project-button relative z-10 text-gray-300 bg-site-red font-bold rounded-lg text-sm px-6 py-3 inline-flex overflow-hidden group transition duration-300 uppercase"
          >
            <span class="flex items-center gap-2 button-text text-sm relative z-10 w-full text-center uppercase"
              >See other projects <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="size-4"
              >
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"></path>
              </svg>
            </span>
            <span class="absolute inset-0 bg-red-600 transition-transform duration-500 ease-in-out translate-x-full group-hover:translate-x-0"></span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Carousel -->

      <div class="min-h-[350px] relative">
        <div class="container mx-auto w-full overflow-hidden relative">
          <div class="w-full h-full absolute">
            <div class="w-1/4 h-full absolute z-30 left-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to right, rgb(22, 31, 42), rgba(22, 31, 42, 0));"></div>
            <div class="w-1/4 h-full absolute z-30 right-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to left, rgb(31, 41, 55), rgba(22, 31, 42, 0));"></div>
          </div>

          <div id="logo-slider" class="logo-slider overflow-hidden">
            <div class="marquee">
              <div
                class="carousel-items flex items-center justify-center"
                style="width: fit-content; animation: carouselAnim 10s infinite alternate linear;"
