                  <span class="text-gray-300 font-bold mb-3 p-2 md:text-left text-center">Entrance exam <br /> (1st semester project)</span>
                  <img class="h-[200px] w-[200px] rounded-full shadow-2xl object-cover" src="images/entrance_exam.webp" alt="Entrance exam" />
